        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Writer Betsy Copping Corner, wife of endocrinologist George Washington Corner, covered medical history and wrote book reviews; she also edited the diary of William Shippen, Jr. and the letters of John Fothergill.</p>
